"{\"uid\": \"benzinga.com-news-24-07-39987622-arson-attack-targets-paris-railways-ahead-of-olympics-opening-ceremony-what-you-need-to-know\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The high-speed rail system in France, the host of the 2024 Summer Olympics, was the target of coordinated arson attacks on Friday ahead of theevent's opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 30, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9885763547699725, \"rank\": 0.006649972565090156, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What Happened:The attacks were carried out on Friday morning.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 230, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"French Prime MinisterGabriel Attaldivulged information about the attacks in aposton X.\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9393617923960054, \"rank\": 0.05338463319670927, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Early this morning, acts of sabotage were carried out in a prepared and coordinated manner on SNCF installations,\\\" Attal said.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The consequences on the rail network are massive and serious.\\\"\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While officials have not yet determined if the attacks were an instance of organized terror, Attal expressed a strong desire to establish the identity of the arsonists.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our intelligence services and law enforcement are mobilized to find and punish the perpetrators of these criminal acts.\\\"\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Accordingto the New York Times, the attacks will disrupt transportation for over 1 million passengers over the weekend before the train lines can be repaired.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 821, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999986336547648, \"rank\": 1.159956177176702e-06, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fires were set in pipes carrying cables, making repairs difficult, and were detected around 4 a.m.  Why it Matters: The Olympics is a biannual event that draws participants and fans from around the world.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials are still planning on hosting the opening ceremony on Friday, though many athletes and fans may not be able to attend.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The railway disruptions will likely make it harder for fans to attend the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris officials are on high alert for potential threats, with additional security presence and fortification,accordingto the Los Angeles Times.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996923634, \"rank\": 3.0760825298385993e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"ht